quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  7,150,"Mi d iu$al Musa ar ugdud is, s wurrif akked lĂȘemĂ»a, inna: \"ay d ucmit wayen is iyi tneĂ»fem, deffir iw! Teb$am a d i$iwwel lameĂŽ n Mass nnwen\"? IveggeĂŽ tilewĂȘin, iĂźĂźef gma s seg uqeĂŽĂŽu, ijebt it id $uĂŽes. Inna d: \"a mmi s n yimma, s tidep, iĂȘqeĂŽ iyi ugdud, qĂŽib iyi n$an. Ur ssefĂŽaĂȘ icenga yissi. Ur iyi pparra seg ugdud imednas"
  7,151,"Inna: \"a Mass iw! SemmeĂȘ ane$, nek akked gma, Ssekcem a$ ar uĂȘunu K. KeĂ§Ă§, Tifev akw wid ipĂȘunun"
  7,152,"Ih, wid iĂąabden aĂąajmi, a d i$li fellasen wurrif n Mass nnsen, ad ndellen di tmeddurt n ddunit. Akka ay NepqeĂźĂźi wid id isnulfuyen"
  7,153,"Wid ixedmen tucmitin, sinna, steĂŽoĂąen deffir sent, u umnen, Mass ik, s tidep, deffir sent, ar IpsemmiĂȘ, IpĂȘunu"
  7,154,"Mi irs wurrif is, iddem ed Musa tilewĂȘin. Di tira nnsent, nnhaya akked uĂȘunu i wid ippagwaden Mass nnsen"
  7,155,"Ifren ed Musa Ă»atet irgazen seg ugdud is, ad mlilen yidneÂŁ. Mi ten tewwet zzenzla, inna: \"a Mass iw! Lemmer i K ihwi, yili, iu$ lĂȘal, Ten$iv ten, u Tegliv yissi. Day ad a$ TemĂȘuv, ilmend n wayen xedmen ije$lufen segne$? Wagi d ahewwel iK kan, Tettellifev syis win i K ihwan, Tnehhuv win i K ihwan. KeĂ§Ă§ d Bab nne$, SemmeĂȘ a$, Ăun fella$, KeĂ§Ă§ Tifev akw wid ipsemmiĂȘen"
